{
  "id": "684802a1b14353490777db30",
  "title": "デライトの＆ボタン",
  "created": 1749549733,
  "updated": 1781209574,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "684802a1b14353490777db30",
      "text": "デライトの＆ボタン",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549733,
      "updated": 1749550217
    },
    {
      "id": "6848048b000000000042f265",
      "text": "[デライト]でログインしているときに、[デライトの検索]窓に表示されるようになるボタン",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1749550220,
      "updated": 1781181917
    },
    {
      "id": "684804cd000000000042f268",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550286,
      "updated": 1749550286
    },
    {
      "id": "684804ce000000000042f269",
      "text": "機能：自分の輪郭のみの表示と、全員の輪郭の表示とを切り替える",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1749550287,
      "updated": 1781182074
    },
    {
      "id": "68480330000000000042f25c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549872,
      "updated": 1749549872
    },
    {
      "id": "68480331000000000042f25d",
      "text": "「＆」ボタン",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549873,
      "updated": 1749549889
    },
    {
      "id": "684802a4000000000042f259",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d284f2127b079ab097be3256985e6abd]",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549733,
      "updated": 1749549866
    },
    {
      "id": "6848032a000000000042f25b",
      "text": "\t「[輪郭]」は[デライト]における投稿単位",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549866,
      "updated": 1749549983
    },
    {
      "id": "68480450000000000042f261",
      "text": "\t押すと「＆」が緑色になり、自分の輪郭のリストを一覧できる",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550160,
      "updated": 1749550190
    },
    {
      "id": "6848046d000000000042f262",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/c905495da14356cdea8323ff77d09a4c]",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550190,
      "updated": 1749550190
    },
    {
      "id": "6848046e000000000042f263",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550190,
      "updated": 1749550190
    },
    {
      "id": "68480478000000000042f264",
      "text": " 他の人＆",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550201,
      "updated": 1749550211
    },
    {
      "id": "6848032a000000000042f25a",
      "text": " \t[https://gyazo.com/cb983dafb894b11b11af928b67b437a8]",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749549866,
      "updated": 1749550211
    },
    {
      "id": "68480405000000000042f260",
      "text": " \t\t分かりにくいけど、他の人のページをサンプルにするわけにもいかないので、自分のものを例に[久住哲.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550085,
      "updated": 1749550211
    },
    {
      "id": "68480405000000000042f25f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0e769da385ed001ecc1fc1",
      "created": 1749550085,
      "updated": 1749550085
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aae8e0000000000d3659a",
      "text": "思考のenvironmentを一発で切り替えれるような感覚で好き[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781182095,
      "updated": 1781182141
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aae8f0000000000d3659b",
      "text": " 仮想環境の切り替えに近い",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781182095,
      "updated": 1781182167
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2aaec40000000000d3659c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1781182149,
      "updated": 1781182149
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b180b000000000082e1d3",
      "text": " 検索状態の見通しをよくするために実は[検索演算子]として実装されている「文字として扱えるボタン」[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209138,
      "updated": 1781209512
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b183e000000000082e1d5",
      "text": "  バックスペースで消せるしキーボードで入力できる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209188,
      "updated": 1781209232
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b1869000000000082e1d6",
      "text": "  左側に利用者の知番を置くとその利用者とのAND検索になる",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209232,
      "updated": 1781209313
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b18bb000000000082e1d7",
      "text": "   知番を省略すると自分とのAND検索になる、というわけ",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209315,
      "updated": 1781209337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b18d2000000000082e1d8",
      "text": "  [ギミック]としては洒落ているが、初見では分かりにくいらしく混乱する人もいるのがちょっと課題",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209337,
      "updated": 1781209574
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2b180b000000000082e1d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781209138,
      "updated": 1781209138
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9c1640000000000bfcb71",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777975654,
      "updated": 1777975655
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9c1650000000000bfcb72",
